name: Once Upon a Time in the Future: Prapatan Jenxxxkol 2009
description:
It's also about paying homage to the '80s retrofuture. Using CGA graphics 4 colours pixel animation style. 

Tells about everyday life in a place called Prapatan Jenxxxkol in 2009. With activities from residents who are quite varied. Such as breakdancing, sitting in the park doing fart activities, etc.
